## STEP 1 — GitHub Push

Run these commands in your terminal (replace TOKEN with your GitHub Personal Access Token):

```bash
cd /home/claude/vittaiq

# If you have a PAT:
git remote set-url origin https://<YOUR_GITHUB_TOKEN>@github.com/arun952137-afk/vittaiq.git
git push -u origin main

# OR use GitHub Desktop / upload the folder directly at github.com/new
```

**Create PAT at:** https://github.com/settings/tokens → New token → Repo scope

---

## STEP 2 — Vercel Deploy

**Option A — Vercel Dashboard (Recommended)**
1. Go to https://vercel.com/new
2. Import Git Repository → connect GitHub
3. Select `vittaiq` repo
4. Framework: Next.js (auto-detected)
5. Add these Environment Variables:
   ```
   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL = https://xkjapruluyoyziateghv.supabase.co
   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = eyJhbGci...akoQk
   OPENAI_API_KEY = sk-YOUR-KEY-HERE
   ```
6. Click Deploy

**Option B — Vercel CLI**
```bash
cd /home/claude/vittaiq
npx vercel login    # opens browser
npx vercel --prod   # deploys
```

---

## STEP 3 — Add OpenAI API Key

After deployment:
1. Vercel Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
2. Add: `OPENAI_API_KEY` = `sk-your-real-key`
3. Redeploy (Settings → Deployments → Redeploy)

**Get key at:** https://platform.openai.com/api-keys

---

## STEP 4 — Supabase Verification

Your Supabase project is live at:
- URL: https://xkjapruluyoyziateghv.supabase.co
- Dashboard: https://supabase.com/dashboard/project/xkjapruluyoyziateghv

